      <title>纽约即将就租户保护和开发商税收减免的住房政策达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/ny-budget-deal-near-with-tenant-protections-developer-tax-break</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，纽约州多年来最彻底的住房政策变化即将在州立法机构中获得通过，预算协议预计将超过 2,330 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/ny-budget-deal-near-with-tenant-protections-developer-tax-break</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 18:10:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
