      <title>巴克莱表示，遭受重创的美国债券值得一看</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/beaten-up-build-america-bonds-are-worth-a-look-barclays-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行敦促投资者关注“建设美国债券”，该债券在过去几个月中普遍走软，因为少数发行人提前赎回证券，给债务持有人带来了潜在损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/beaten-up-build-america-bonds-are-worth-a-look-barclays-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 17:57:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
